                    <h3>Overview</h3>
                    <p>Risk Integrity Management (RIM) is a specialized risk-consulting firm offering expert services in: Insurance Operations Management SIU/Fraud Consulting Risk Integrity Programs and Risk Control Services...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Other tab content sections can be added here -->
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
